  <p><strong>0.999... = 1</strong></p>

  <p>Need proof?</p>
  <pre>
Let x = 0.999...
Then, 10x = 9.999...
Subtract: 10x - x = 9.999... - 0.999...
Result: 9x = 9 â†’ x = 1
